                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 826/122.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to Chargé
                            <persName type="to">Janes</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1909-01-20">
                            <hi rend="italic">January 20, 1909</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr. Root instructs Mr. Janes to express the appreciation of the United States for
                    the continuance of tariff reduction.</p>
            </div>
